Package com.kremerk.Sqlite.Annotations

Annotation Types Summary
AutoIncrement Allows for specifying a field as Auto Incremented on a POJO that "maps" to a database table.
OneToMany Allows for specifying a field as a One To Many relationship.
PrimaryKey Allows for specifying a field as a Primary key on a POJO that "maps" to a database table.
